column5: Wondering if anyone would share information on the Winnipeg River and out on the lake out of Pine Falls? Interested in the water level, water temperature, if the shiners have moved into the system and on how the fishing has been. Any information is much appreciated. Thanks in advance.
Is there anyone out there willing to share an update on the river / lake? Curious on river / lake levels, amount of current, and how the fishing is. Appreciate any input. Thanks in advance.
